      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>CARRAMERICA REALTY CORP., Washington, a real estate developer, bought three office properties and land in suburban Atlanta for $58.6 million. It did not disclose the sellers.</p>
        <p>MELLON BANK CORP., Pittsburgh, said it planned to split its stock 2 for 1 and increase its quarterly dividend by 10 percent.</p>
